    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring mechanical grip out of every apex. The chassis has been inspected for subframe integrity, and the suspension retains its original geometry for that signature analog feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system refresh, ensuring the valvetrain remains quiet and the high-compression head remains within thermal tolerances. A mechanically sound icon ready for the backroads.",
