      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a blend of performance and reliability. Finished in a deep metallic charcoal that still catches the light beautifully, the exterior has been kept in impressive shape, showing only the expected minor stone chips on the front valence from highway commuting. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the charcoal leather seats have been treated regularly, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system and the power sunroof\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained with a complete folder of service records to prove it. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and a brake inspection, ensuring it\u2019s ready for the road immediately. It shifts smoothly, pulls strong, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has clearly been a point of pride for its previous owners.",
